  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO REQUIRE A PERSON LICENSED TO DO BUSINESS AS A MONEY TRANSMISSION BUSINESS TO COLLECT A FEE FOR EACH TRANSACTION; TO AUTHORIZE THE SUSPENSION OF A LICENSE AS A MONEY TRANSMISSION BUSINESS FOR FAILURE TO COMPLY WITH THE MONEY TRANSMISSION FEE REQUIREMENTS; TO EXEMPT CERTAIN TRANSFERS AND CERTAIN FINANCIAL INSTITUTIONS FROM THE MONEY TRANSMISSION FEE REQUIREMENTS; TO CREATE A TAX CREDIT FOR MONEY TRANSMISSION FEES PAID BY A TAXPAYER DURING THE TAX YEAR; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
  },
